channel.title: To Haven and Akatsuki members
channel.description:
Both our citys and my highway where attacked, Me and David for the most part fixed both of the towns. I didn't get any pictures of the Akatsuki kingdom cause david was working on it or my highway I just fixed it. As for haven I did fix it up but not to the way it was properly(I didn't have enough stuff). Here is a picture of haven.
[IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/290ri9i.png[/img] [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/vo21rk.png[/img]
You will need to replace a few things I believe but I fixed most of your hotel and fountains.
